          <li>Access the metaverse. Answer and create surveys. Earn rewards</li>
          <li>Access real-time data and make informed decisions</li>
          <li>Personalize your experience: create your own avatar and make it stand out</li>
          <li>Join a growing community and voice your opinion</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
